Code preview of table Ponuda

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('PONUDA')
and type = 'U')
drop table PONUDA
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: PONUDA */
/*==============================================================*/
create table PONUDA (
PONUDA_ID numeric(8) not null,
RESURS_ID2 numeric(8) not null,
MULTITEKA_ID2 numeric(5) not null,
POSLOVNA_GODINA_ID numeric(2) not null,
CENA money not null,
DATUM datetime null,
constraint PK_PONUDA primary key nonclustered (MULTITEKA_ID2, RESURS_ID2, POSLOVNA_GODINA_ID, PONUDA_ID)
)
go
